    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering an 8,400 RPM redline and immediate response via individual throttle bodies. Paired with a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock, the mechanical engagement is visceral. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a well-maintained multi-link rear suspension and aluminum subframes. While showing honest character from regular use, the powertrain exhibits strong compression and smooth VANOS operation. Recent preventive maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a fresh throttle actuator set, ensuring this high-revving masterpiece is mechanically prepared for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
