      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a well-maintained example that strikes a perfect balance between performance and practicality. The exterior paint retains a high gloss, complemented by clean alloy wheels, though close inspection may reveal a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is a highlight: it is a non-smoker environment with upholstery that remains firm and free of tears. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in great shape; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent multi-point inspection confirming the brakes and tires have plenty of life remaining. The engine starts promptly and idles quietly, offering a smooth and responsive driving experience. It comes with a complete set of floor mats and two sets of keys. This is a dependable, honest car ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
