    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways! It\u2019s clean, runs smoothly, and I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years. If you\u2019re looking for a solid, dependable car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today, this is the one for you. I'd love for you to come by, take a look, and see how great it feels behind the wheel!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
