      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant, complete with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The suspension retains its precision with refreshed bushings and original dampers, ensuring the chassis remains communicative and balanced. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is in peak operational state, making this an ideal driver's car for the purist enthusiast.",
